short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension to turn phone numbers on pages into click to dial links.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Byphone Number Linkify is a handy chrome extension designed to make it easier to use click to dial with the Byphone Hosted PBX solution. It will auto scan web pages you visit to make it easier to dial any phone numbers on page. You can also highlight a body of text, right click and select "Click to Dial" to extract phone numbers.
